name: Home
description: A communication contact point at a home; attempted contacts for business purposes might intrude privacy and chances are one will contact family or other household members instead of the person one wishes to call. Typically used with urgent cases
column5: or if no other contacts are available.

name: Work
description: An office contact point. First choice for business related contacts during business hours.

name: Temp
description: A temporary contact point. The period can provide more detailed information.

name: Old
description: This contact point is no longer in use (or was never correct

name: Mobile
description: A telecommunication device that moves and stays with its owner. May have characteristics of all other use codes
column6: not the first choice for routine business.

name: Less than
description: The actual value is less than the given value.

name: Less or Equal to
description: The actual value is less than or equal to the given value.

name: Greater than
description: The actual value is greater than the given value.

name: Greater or Equal to
description: The actual value is greater than or equal to the given value.

name: Phone
description: The value is a telephone number used for voice calls. Use of full international numbers starting with + is recommended to enable automatic dialing support but not required.

name: Fax
description: The value is a fax machine. Use of full international numbers starting with + is recommended to enable automatic dialing support but not required.

name: Email
description: The value is an email address.

name: Pager
description: The value is a pager number. These may be local pager numbers that are only usable on a particular pager system.

name: URL
description: A contact that is not a phone
column6: pager or email address and is expressed as a URL. This is intended for various personal contacts including blogs
column10: etc. Do not use for email addresses.

name: SMS
description: A contact that can be used for sending an sms message (e.g. mobile phones

name: Other
description: A contact that is not a phone
column6: page or email address and is not expressible as a URL. E.g. Internal mail address. This SHOULD NOT be used for contacts that are expressible as a URL (e.g. Skype
column9: etc.) Extensions may be used to distinguish 'other' contact types.

name: Good
description: Product represent actual entity supplied by party organizations.

name: Service
description: Product represent services provided by party organizations.

name: Package
description: Product is a package of other products. Usually package created to provide discount to products in the package.

name: Draft
description: Entity in draft state and not ready yet for approval.

name: Pending
description: Entity pending approval and can't be used.

name: Active
description: Entity in active state and can be used.

name: Retired
description: Entity retired and cannot be executed any more.

name: Error
description: Entity in have error and can't be used.

name: Monday
description: First day of the week by ISO 8601.

name: Tuesday
description: Second day of the week by ISO 8601.

name: Wednesday
description: Third day of the week by ISO 8601.

name: Thursday
description: Fourth day of the week by ISO 8601.

name: Friday
description: Fifth day of the week by ISO 8601.

name: Saturday
description: Sixth day of the week by ISO 8601.

name: Sunday
description: Seventh day of the week by ISO 8601.

name: Goods
description: Product line represent goods supplied by party organizations.

name: Services
description: Product line represent services provided by party organizations.

name: Goods And Services
description: Product line contains mix of product  of goods and services.

name: Supplier
description: Party to supply products to the network or other network party. Product defined by supplier and his contract with network.

name: Distributor
description: Party distribute product from supplier. Distributor can use general contract of supplier with network or sign specific contract for distribution.

name: Provider
description: Party define product or service and deliver it to consumer. Provider contract specify conditions of providing services through the network.

name: Network
description: Network party facilitate product distribution. Network organized and managed parties contract and support parties execution.

name: ERP
description: Corporate ERP system used in company.

name: UYI
description: Uruguay Peso en Unidades Indexadas (URUIURUI) (funds code)

name: XBC
description: European Unit of Account 9 (E.U.A.-9) (bond market unit)

name: Network
description: Contract to supply or distribute products to the network.

name: Party
description: Contract to distribute or supply product signed by parties directly. It allows party to negotiate favorable compare to general distribution.

name: Healthcare
description: Product and services from healthcare industry.
